      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 2.1M, medium 5.8M, fine 14.2M cells). GCI for the relative hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point was 2.3%, below the 5% threshold. Richardson extrapolation confirmed asymptotic convergence. Achieved level 3 reflects the systematic three-mesh GCI study exceeding minimum Gradation 2 requirements."
