      "rationale": "FDA experimental test conditions for the generic centrifugal blood pump are fully documented in Morrison et al. (2012). Inlet flow rates (2–7 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), and outlet pressures were replicated in simulation boundary conditions. Temperature and fluid properties (bovine blood surrogate) matched within reported experimental uncertainty."
