      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the direct regulatory QoI used to compare the subject device against the predicate. Wall shear stress and scalar stress distributions are mechanistically linked to red blood cell damage and provide diagnostic insight into hemolysis-generating regions. QoI selection is consistent with FDA guidance on pump hemolysis assessment."
